    "body": "## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nStart debugging your app by running it on multiple devices (ios simulator, android simulator). Upon Save, only the active devices is hot-reloaded. \r\n\r\nCan this be extended that it reloads all running devices?\r\n\r\n`flutter run -d all` will hot-reload all devices when started in terminal and pressing \"s\".\r\n\r\nCan this be included in the IDE upon Save.\r\n",
